'''凱爾·理查·弗里蘭'''（{{lang-en|Kyle Richard Freeland}}，{{bd|1993年|5月14日|}}），為美國職棒大聯盟的投手，目前效力於科羅拉多洛磯。他在[[2014年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2014年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]的第一輪第8順位被洛磯隊選走。
==職業生涯==
[[2014年美國職棒大聯盟選秀|2014年美國職棒大聯盟選秀]]，洛磯隊在第一輪第8順位選進弗里蘭。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/kyle-freeland-is-college-baseballs-fastest-rising-draft-prospect-1398293172|title=Evansville's Kyle Freeland Is College Baseball's Fastest-Rising Draft Prospect|author=Michael Salfino|date=April 23, 2014|work=The Wall Street Journal|access-date=November 17, 2017|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213170211/https://www.wsj.com/articles/kyle-freeland-is-college-baseballs-fastest-rising-draft-prospect-1398293172}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/70934150/freeland-continues-to-carve-up-opposing-hitters/|title=Freeland continues to carve up opposing hitters|work=Major League Baseball|access-date=November 17, 2017|archive-date=2017-11-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171117122054/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/70934150/freeland-continues-to-carve-up-opposing-hitters/}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140605&content_id=78417034&notebook_id=78424668&vkey=notebook_col&c_id=col|author=Thomas Harding|title=Rockies take college lefty with local roots in Round 1|work=Colorado Rockies|date=June 5, 2014|access-date=November 17, 2017|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715174325/http://mlb.mlb.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20140605&content_id=78417034&notebook_id=78424668&vkey=notebook_col&c_id=col}}</ref>該年他在新人聯盟和1A拿下3勝0敗，防禦率1.15的成績。

2015年，他升上高階1A的[[莫德斯托樫果|莫德斯托樫果]]。隔年順利升上2A與3A，他在2016年拿下11勝10敗，防禦率3.89。<ref>[http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=607536#/career/R/pitching/2016/ALL Kyle Freeland] {{Wayback|url=http://www.milb.com/player/index.jsp?player_id=607536#/career/R/pitching/2016/ALL |date=20190725224616 }} Retrieved November 17, 2017.</ref>

2017年4月7日，弗里蘭升上大聯盟。他順利拿下大聯盟首勝，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.mlb.com/news/article/20170407222892770/rockies-kyle-freeland-quiets-dodgers-bats/?game_pk=490154|author=Ken Gurnick|author2=Thomas Harding|title=Freeland dazzles in debut as Rox down LA|date=April 7, 2017|website=MLB.com|access-date=November 16, 2017|archive-date=2017-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170730150334/http://m.mlb.com/news/article/20170407222892770/rockies-kyle-freeland-quiets-dodgers-bats/?game_pk=490154}}</ref>同時他還敲出大聯盟首安。<ref name=espn>{{cite web|url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=370407127|title=Freeland wins debut as Rockies top Dodgers 2-1|agency=[[Associated_Press|Associated Press]]|publisher=[[ESPN|ESPN]]|date=April 8, 2017|access-date=November 17, 2017|archive-date=2018-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143544/http://www.espn.com/mlb/recap?gameId=370407127}}</ref>而他也成為大聯盟51年來首位在家鄉球隊完成初登板的先發投手。<ref name=espn/>5月21日，他敲出大聯盟首轟。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Kyle Freeland Career Home Runs|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/event_hr.fcgi?id=freelky01&t=b|website=Baseball-Reference.com|language=en|access-date=2020-05-04|archive-date=2017-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171101123417/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/event_hr.fcgi?id=freelky01&t=b}}</ref>7月9日，他曾面對白襪隊投出8.1局的無安打。這年他拿下11勝11敗。

2018年是弗里蘭破繭而出的一年，這年他拿下17勝9敗，而且防禦率2.84寫下隊史單季新低。雖然他開季先吞下3敗，不過最後他仍投出好成績。其中他在主場更是只有2.40的防禦率，寫下隊史新紀錄。而他也在賽揚獎票選中拿下第4名。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.denverpost.com/2018/09/29/german-marquez-kyle-freeland-rockies-duo/|title=Saunders: German Marquez’s fire, Kyle Freeland’s ice give Rockies best pitching duo in club history|date=September 29, 2018|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813050750/https://www.denverpost.com/2018/09/29/german-marquez-kyle-freeland-rockies-duo/}}</ref>

[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽]]，弗里蘭先發6.2局無失分。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/nl-wild-card-game-how-kyle-freeland-and-the-rockies-neutralized-one-of-the-cubs-most-dangerous-hitters/|title=NL Wild Card Game: How Kyle Freeland and the Rockies neutralized one of the Cubs' most dangerous hitters|website=CBSSports.com|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2018-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181004124429/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/nl-wild-card-game-how-kyle-freeland-and-the-rockies-neutralized-one-of-the-cubs-most-dangerous-hitters/}}</ref>最終洛磯2比1於延長13局險勝小熊，弗里蘭也成為隊史首位在季後賽先發無失分的投手。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2018/10/03/mlb-playoffs-cubs-rockies-joe-maddon-nl-wild-card/1506659002/|title=Winter is here: Stunned Cubs prepare for change after shocking postseason elimination|first=Bob|last=Nightengale|website=USA TODAY|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222062339/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/columnist/bob-nightengale/2018/10/03/mlb-playoffs-cubs-rockies-joe-maddon-nl-wild-card/1506659002/}}</ref>


2019年，他開季拿下2勝6敗，防禦率7.13。因此他在5月底被下放3A調整。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2019/05/rockies-option-kyle-freeland.html|title=Rockies Option Kyle Freeland|website=MLB Trade Rumors|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2020-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201030231919/https://www.mlbtraderumors.com/2019/05/rockies-option-kyle-freeland.html}}</ref>最終他整年只投出3勝11敗，防禦率6.73。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/f/freelky01.shtml|title=Kyle Freeland Stats|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-02-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210217104509/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/f/freelky01.shtml}}</ref>

2020年，弗里蘭觸底反彈。這季因為疫情只有60場例行賽，而他先發13場，拿下2勝3敗，防禦率4.33。雖然帳面成績普普，不過他成為國聯單季最多次優質先發的投手(9次)。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2020-standard-pitching.shtml|title=2020 National League Standard Pitching|website=Baseball-Reference.com|access-date=2021-02-06|archive-date=2021-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210131042315/https://www.baseball-reference.com/leagues/NL/2020-standard-pitching.shtml}}</ref>
